---
title: Ultimate THIS™ Isn't Chicken Tikka Masala with Spinach, Basmati Rice and Crispy Shallot Topping
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate THIS™ Isn't Chicken Tikka Masala is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.
